me":"2019-11-18T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"仲有人相信左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左膠見到藍絲有危險<br />\n再打會死！唔好再打<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TemFoaQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTemFoaQ.jpg&h=02bd1e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左膠見到黑警有危險<br />\n包紮再護送到安全地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/str2BMv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fstr2BMv.jpg&h=de277238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左膠見到手足有危險<br />\n不了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J0dcYZ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ0dcYZ3.jpg&h=8a14e127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左膠見到大肚婆有危險<br />\n不了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mYH5ziA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmYH5ziA.jpg&h=7b48b0be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左膠見到學生有危險<br />\n不了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBGaLo8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBGaLo8.png&h=e2a94358&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ad0d5f772ff9b0256385e0b85ffd4f068f69d9c","tid":1734622,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"由裝修到火魔法越嚟越多, 和你飛嘅支援就越來越少, 鬼唔知和你飛全面進場可以救到理大, 但由616到宜加已經少咗好多喎你飛support, 仲屌鳩人左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a725fc2ba07bfe343f6ce8863f0586cfa57524b","tid":1734622,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:17:33.000Z","msg":"推理大媽咪會"},{"pid":"2bae5994245ee8901313ad4fda53a9806e933bdd","tid":1734622,"uid":305083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:20:30.000Z","msg":"好想推但p 牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102be93cc0e9f4830b4353f5d5f463f5f3bb08e2","tid":1734622,"uid":186088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:20:46.000Z","msg":"試試佢"},{"pid":"56cb5682b2c134399df835969d3913c6665bfc87","tid":1734622,"uid":286033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"推唔郁啊都推"},{"pid":"5c5fa3b075b788b770ba47af43938bd724d1842a","tid":1734622,"uid":217897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:40:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8dd68398d0a457c886a1cb6d5dd202d68791a43f","tid":1734622,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T14:16:35.000Z","msg":"幫推 左膠全面進場 <br />\n<br />\n平時咁鍾意幫被私了廢老 <br />\n<br />\n依家快啲幫學生"},{"pid":"341cdaec4fd93c880aa5893db059000f8da0c3ec","tid":1734622,"uid":313839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"無力一推<br />\n咩都要試"},{"pid":"e3e8e05cbcc1e526d5e66a3d4d84d2b087ba0ec8","tid":1734622,"uid":289963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"P牌 都要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868820df065e0c45f997d3e816bd700eb2f34397","tid":1734622,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:13:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}